  RFC4096 [label="RFC4096
Policy-Mandated Labels Such as Adv: in
Email Subject Headers Considered
Ineffective At Best
2005", shape=ellipse, fillcolor="#e8f0ff", tooltip="This memo discusses policies that require certain labels to be inserted in the Subject: header of a mail message.  Such policies are difficult to specify accurately while remaining compliant with key RFCs and are likely to be ineffective at best.  This memo discusses an alternate, \%standards-compliant approach that is significantly simpler to specify and is somewhat less likely to be ineffective.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.", style=filled, fillcolor=green]; 

